snippet.title: Rival Rides - Official Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Rival Rides is an exciting multiplayer VR game where players can compete in a variety of games and go on wild rides. Collect the highest amount of golden egg trophies and become the champion. Rival Rides is available now on PC.
